<item>
            <title>[LU-6459] Backport ZFS on Linux 0.6.4 compat changes to Lustre 2.5</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6459</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ZFS OSD in Lustre 2.5.3 fails to build with the recent 0.6.4 release of ZoL. Fixes for master had been provided in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6038&quot; title=&quot;ZFS 0.6.4 Compatibility&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6038&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6038&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but haven&apos;t been backported to b2_5 yet, as far as I could tell. I&apos;ve done that now and will upload the patches to Gerrit once testing with both ZoL 0.6.3 and 0.6.4 is complete.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
